UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc6='Sul\'thraze... the first time I heard the word uttered I was around your age. It meant nothing to me then, as it means nothing to you now. It was not until a warband of trolls coming from Zul\'Farrak laid waste to the land that I understood... and feared.$B$BMany will tell you that the Splitblade of Suffering does not exist. That it\'s a myth; a rumor started to scare children \'straight.\' But believe me, $r, it exists.$B$B<Trenton loses focus as he runs his hand across the jagged scar on his face.>' WHERE entry=1758; /* Text0_0: Sul\'thraze... the first time I heard the word uttered I was around your age. It meant nothing to me then, as it means nothing to you now. It was not until a warband of trolls coming from Zul\'Farrak laid waste to the land that I understood... and feared.$B$BMany will tell you that the Splitblade of Suffering does not exist. That it\'s a myth; a rumor started to scare children \'straight.\' But believe me, $r, it exists.$B$B<Trenton loses focus as he runs his hand across the jagged scar on his face.> */
